Oireachtas Explorer
===================

This application consumes the Oireachtas Open Data API
(https://api.oireachtas.ie/) and displays information derived from it.

Parliamentary data (debates, divisions, questions, legislation, member
records) is:

  Copyright (c) Houses of the Oireachtas

and is reused under the Oireachtas (Open Data) PSI Licence, which
incorporates the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International Licence
(CC-BY 4.0):

  Licence:    https://www.oireachtas.ie/en/open-data/license/
  CC-BY 4.0:  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

Modifications
-------------
The data displayed by this application has been:

  - filtered, paginated, and re-ordered for display;
  - transformed from the Oireachtas XML/JSON schemas into derived
    summaries (e.g. vote breakdowns, activity totals, speaker filters);
  - combined across multiple API endpoints.

It may therefore not reflect the complete or most current official
record. Authoritative records are available at https://www.oireachtas.ie/.

